  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_SevenFoldFrameRuntimeSelection] is the active semantic stack frame for selecting and building the seven-fold frame runtime
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_seven_fold_frame_runtime_selection
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_topology_map_runtime
  + [child_frame_set] is manager_state, remaining_ready_tasks, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_022, Task_051, seven_fold_frame_runtime, outside_boundary, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is topology_map.py, 2026-06-24_task_048_topology_map_runtime_001.hg.sop, Manager_State.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_022.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is build Task_051 seven-fold frame runtime
  + [question_register] is how to read a subject surface, rank visible correlations, select top three central cells, and emit fold-leg weighted orbit records
  + [delineation_register] is inside remaining ReadyTaskSet, Task_051, subject surface, correlation ranking, central triad, fold legs, weighted orbit, source evidence, outside, and commit cadence
  + [periphery_register] is worker mutation outside, branch creation outside, remote sync outside, hidden-state replay outside, unrelated dirty files outside, credentials outside, and destructive action outside
  + [operation_register] is inspect_seven_fold_pants_correlation_frame_contracts, preserve_source, build_runtime, add_tests, emit_seven_fold_frame, validate, commit, push, emit_next_tick
  + [evidence_register] is Manager_State completed Task_142, topology map runtime, generated topology map graph, and operating_loop_tick_022
  + [wisdom_register] is Codex should add seven-fold frame runtime as the next bridge from sparse topology cells into top-three heat ordering and fold-leg weighted orbit records
  + [caution_register] is seven-fold frame runtime must not treat weighted central correlations as proof of truth or exact transformer geometry
  + [balance_register] is stable because Task_048 completed with tests and semantic-proxy boundaries visible
  + [integration_register] is Task_048 completed and Task_051 selected as next runtime task
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

